  <title>How to approach this book </title>
  <p>
Please follow the sections of this book in order, You should start here and from here use the next button to move to the later sections. Each section of this book builds on the previous one. Skipping ahead makes the material harder to understand.
In the following sessions, you will see some video lectures. Please watch them carefully. You can enlarge the window to view the code examples clearly. If needed, click the settings icon in the video player and set the quality to 1080p for better clarity. 
  </p>
<p>
After watching the videos, carefully answer the checkpoint questions and complete all the activities. After answering questions, make sure to check your response for correctness. If your answer was not correct, please try again until you get it right. These questions are part of the instruction. 
</p>


